"2500,1696\" data-comments-opened=\"0\" data-image-meta=\"{\"aperture\":\"0\",\"credit\":\"Photo Copyright Monica Mares \\/ Supplied by John Chapple \\/ www.JohnChapple.com n\",\"camera\":\"\",\"caption\":\"July 27, 2016. Clovis, New Mexico. Old family pictures of Caleb Peterson who is in a sexual relationship with her biological son, Monica Mares...Photo Copyright Monica Mares \\/ Supplied by John Chapple \\/ www.JohnChapple.com\",\"created_timestamp\":\"0\",\"copyright\":\"\",\"focal_length\":\"0\",\"iso\":\"0\",\"shutter_speed\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\",\"orientation\":\"0\"}\" data-image-title=\"AD_215315338.jpg\" data-image-description=\"<p>July 27, 2016. Clovis, New Mexico. Old family pictures of Caleb Peterson who is in a sexual relationship with her biological son, Monica Mares…Photo Copyright Monica Mares / Supplied by John Chapple / www.JohnChapple.com</p> \" data-medium-file=\"https://metrouk2.files.wordpress.com/2016/08/ad_215315338.jpg?quality=80&strip=all&w=300&strip=all\" data-large-file=\"https://metrouk2.files.wordpress.com/2016/08/ad_215315338.jpg?quality=80&strip=all&w=1024&strip=all\" class=\"img-align-none size-full wp-image-6056775\" src=\"https://metrouk2.files.wordpress.com/2016/08/ad_215315338.jpg?quality=80&strip=all&strip=all\" alt=\"July 27, 2016. Clovis, New Mexico. Old family pictures of Caleb Peterson who is in a sexual relationship with her biological son, Monica Mares...Photo Copyright Monica Mares / Supplied by John Chapple / www.JohnChapple.com\" width=\"1024\" height=\"695\" /></div><figcaption>Caleb when he was born, before his adoption (Picture: Monica Mares/John Chapple)</figcaption></figure> She met him for the first time since at Christmas 2015, after the pair got in touch over Facebook.\n<a href=\"http://metro.co.uk/2017/03/20/children-find-parents-dead-from-drug-overdoses-after-they-werent-woken-for-school-6522843\" data-track=\"zone-post-thumbnail-link\" data-track-destination=\"6522843\" class=\"thumbnail-link\"><img src=\"http://i2.wp.com/metrouk2.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/pri_33980891.jpg?crop=68px%2C0px%2C1066px%2C799px&resize=150%2C113&quality=80&strip=all&ssl=1&w=100&h=75\" data-aspect=\"1.3274336283186\" class=\"thumbnail-link-image\" data-rewritten=\"false\" /><span class=\"mor-title\">Children find parents dead from 'drug overdoses' after they weren't woken for school</span></a> Caleb moved in with her and says he fell in love with her in part because she looked after him.\n‘I never had anyone cook me meals or give me anything,’ he told the <a href=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3725551/Mother-36-son-19-fell-love-met-year-gave-adoption-baby-say-willing-risk-JAIL-defend-love.html?ito=social-facebook\" target=\"_blank\">Daily Mail</a>. ‘I never got anything my entire life and she went out of her way to make me happy.\n‘After about a week or so I started having feelings for her, and I guess I fell in love.’\n<figure class=\"alignnone img-container shareable-item\" style=\"max-width:620px\"><div class=\"img-wrap\"><a id=\"item-attachment_6056777\" class=\"anchor\"></a><div class=\"item-share-buttons item-share\"><a class=\"share-item share-item-facebook btn\" title=\"Share this on Facebook\" data-track=\"share-item-facebook\"><span class=\"icon icon-facebook\"></span></a><a class=\"share-item share-item-twitter btn\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Share this on Twitter\" data-track=\"share-item-twitter\"><span class=\"icon icon-twitter\"></span></a><a class=\"share-item share-item-pinterest btn\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Share this on Pinterest\" data-track=\"share-item-pinterest\"><span class=\"icon icon-pinterest\"></span></a></div><img data-attachment-id=\"6056777\" data-permalink=\"http://metro.co.uk/?attachment_id=6056777\" data-orig-file=\"https://metrouk2.files.wordpress.com/2016/08/ad_215315352.jpg?quality=80&strip=all&strip=all\" data-orig-size=\"2500,1668\" data-comments-opened=\"0\" data-image-meta=\"{\"aperture\":\"0\",\"credit\":\"Photo Copyright John Chapple \\/ www.JohnChapple.comn\",\"camera\":\"\",\"caption\":\"July 27, 2016. Clovis, New Mexico. Monica Mares who is in a sexual relationship with her biological son, Caleb Peterson...Photo Copyright John Chapple \\/ www.JohnChapple.com\",\"created_timestamp\":\"0\",\"copyright\":\"\",\"focal_length\":\"0\",\"iso\":\"0\",\"shutter_speed\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\",\"orientation\":\"0\"}\" data-image-title=\"AD_215315352.jpg\" data-image-description=\"<p>July 27, 2016. Clovis, New Mexico. Monica Mares who is in a sexual relationship with her biological son, Caleb Peterson…Photo Copyright John Chapple / www.JohnChapple.com</p> \" data-medium-file=\"https://metrouk2.files.wordpress.com/2016/08/ad_215315352.jpg?quality=80&strip=all&w=300&strip=all\" data-large-file=\"https://metrouk2.files.wordpress.com/2016/08/ad_215315352.jpg?quality=80&strip=all&w=1024&strip=all\" class=\"img-align-none size-full wp-image-6056777\" src=\"https://metrouk2.files.wordpress.com/2016/08/ad_215315352.jpg?quality=80&strip=all&strip=all\" alt=\"July 27, 2016. Clovis, New Mexico. Monica Mares who is in a sexual relationship with her biological son, Caleb Peterson...Photo Copyright John Chapple / www.JohnChapple.com\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" /></div><figcaption>Monica was told to stay away from her nine other children (Picture: John Chapple)</figcaption></figure> The mother-of-nine reciprocated, and now says she would readily give up the right to see her other children if she was asked to choose between them and Caleb.\n‘The first time we were physical we ended up holding hands, and then we ended up kissing – and the kissing led to other things,’ she said.\n‘I felt comfortable with him and we fell even more deeply in love.’\n<div class=\"metro-factbox full\"> <h3 class=\"metro-factbox-title pink exclamation\">What is Genetic Sexual Attraction?</h3> <div class=\"metro-factbox-content pink\"></p> GSA is defined as sexual attraction between close relatives who first meet as adults.\nFor example, if the couple are siblings or half-siblings, a parent or offspring, or first or second cousins.\nHowever, incest is a crime in all 50 US states, as well as in the UK.\n</div> </div> <figure class=\"alignnone img-container shareable-item\" style=\"max-width:620px\"><div class=\"img-wrap\"><a id=\"item-attachment_6058123\" class=\"anchor\"></a><div class=\"item-share-buttons item-share\"><a class=\"share-item share-item-facebook btn\" title=\"Share this on Facebook\" data-track=\"share-item-facebook\"><span class=\"icon icon-facebook\"></span></a><a class=\"share-item share-item-twitter btn\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Share this on Twitter\" data-track=\"share-item-twitter\"><span class=\"icon icon-twitter\"></span></a><a class=\"share-item share-item-pinterest btn\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Share this on Pinterest\" data-track=\"share-item-pinterest\"><span class=\"icon icon-pinterest\"></span></a></div><a href=\"https://metrouk2.files.wordpress.com/2016/08/ad_215360932.jpg?quality=80&strip=all&strip=all\"><img data-attachment-id=\"6058123\" data-permalink=\"http://metro.co.uk/?attachment_id=6058123\" data-orig-file=\"https://metrouk2.files.wordpress.com/2016/08/ad_215360932.jpg?quality=80&strip=all&strip=all\" data-orig-size=\"2500,1668\" data-comments-opened=\"0\" data-image-meta=\"{\"aperture\":\"0\",\"credit\":\"Photo Copyright John Chapple \\/ www.JohnChapple.comn\",\"camera\":\"\",\"caption\":\"July 27, 2016. Clovis, New Mexico. Monica Mares who is in a sexual relationship with her biological son, Caleb Peterson...Photo Copyright John Chapple \\/ www.JohnChapple.com\",\"created_timestamp\":\"0\",\"copyright\":\"\",\"focal_length\":\"0\",\"iso\":\"0\",\"shutter_speed\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\",\"orientation\":\"0\"}\" data-image-title=\"AD_215360932.jpg\" data-image-description=\"<p>July 27, 2016. Clovis, New Mexico. Monica Mares who is in a sexual relationship with her biological son, Caleb Peterson…Photo Copyright John Chapple / www.JohnChapple.com</p> \" data-medium-file=\"https://metrouk2.files.wordpress.com/2016/08/ad_215360932.jpg?quality=80&strip=all&w=300&strip=all\" data-large-file=\"https://metrouk2.files.wordpress.com/2016/08/ad_215360932.jpg?quality=80&strip=all&w=1024&strip=all\" class=\"img-align-center size-full wp-image-6058123\" src=\"https://metrouk2.files.wordpress.com/2016/08/ad_215360932.jpg?quality=80&strip=all&strip=all\" alt=\"July 27, 2016. Clovis, New Mexico. Monica Mares who is in a sexual relationship with her biological son, Caleb Peterson...Photo Copyright John Chapple / www.JohnChapple.com\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" /></a></div><figcaption>Monica Maresoutside her trailer (Picture: John Chapple/ Daily Mail)</figcaption></figure> \nBut Mares says she’s afraid to go out because people in her town know about the relationship, and threaten her and call her names.\n<a href=\"http://metro.co.uk/2017/03/20/us-plans-to-ban-passengers-from-12-countries-from-carrying-electronic-devices-6522856\" data-track=\"zone-post-thumbnail-link\" data-track-destination=\"6522856\" class=\"thumbnail-link\"><img src=\"http://i2.wp.com/metrouk2.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/royal_jordanian-airbus_a340-200-yul-2009.jpg?crop=68px%2C0px%2C1066px%2C799px&resize=150%2C113&quality=80&strip=all&ssl=1&w=100&h=75\" data-aspect=\"1.3274336283186\" class=\"thumbnail-link-image\" data-rewritten=\"false\" /><span class=\"mor-title\">US 'to ban passengers from 12 countries from carrying electronic devices'</span></a> Caleb’s personal life has suffered too. Since the affair became public, his dad walked out on him.\nThe two were interviewed separately so as not to breach their court ordered separation.\nThe teenager said: ‘If I could speak to her now, I would say to her: “I love you and I miss you and I can’t wait to see you again”.’", "external_links": [], "published": "2017-03-21T13:02:00.000+02:00", "crawled": "2017-03-21T08:02:40.742+02:00", "highlightTitle": ""}